{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/11054", "repo": "rails", "body": "This will have a subtle behavioural change if an explicit `nil` is passed. \r\n\r\nBefore, it would change an explicit `nil` to `:invalid`. After, it will keep explicit `nil` as `nil`, and only use `:invalid` if the second argument `message` (and by implication, `options`) was not passed at all.\r\n\r\nNot sure if it matters.", "_id": {"$oid": "5237d926bd3543c15100856c"}, "issue_id": 11054, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/19892443", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11054#issuecomment-19892443", "updated_at": "2013-06-24T07:24:33Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg", "login": "egilburg", "gravatar_id": "cc4f5494a8dcaaf577e678cb3901dab6", "html_url": "https://github.com/egilburg", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/cc4f5494a8dcaaf577e678cb3901dab6?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F552d65b6e9616642fd0217dc7f8361bd.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 242532, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/egilburg/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2013-06-24T07:24:16Z", "id": 19892443, "owner": "rails"}
